query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('unix')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('compiling',
'configuration',
'email',
'environment-variables',
'hard-disk',
'io-redirection',
'kde',
'keyboard-shortcuts',
'network-interface',
'rename',
'system-installation',
'wildcards');
